summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Sixty-four and 50/100 ($64.50) Dollars from the Jackson Street Condemnation Fund, under Ordinance No. 13102, to be paid M. L. Hall, as a refund of sale in error of the North Sixty (60) feet of Lots ten (10) and eleven (11) Block three (3), Syndicate Addition, and directing the City Treasurer to cancel said sale against said property on the Jackson Street Condemnation Roll, under Ordinacne No. 13102.
